@host = http://localhost:62266

### ══════════════════════════════════════════════
### OPTIONAL If-Match (/optional/products)
### Updates proceed even without If-Match header
### ══════════════════════════════════════════════

### 1. Create a product
# @name createOptional
POST {{host}}/optional/products
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Widget",
  "price": 29.99
}

### 2. Get the product — response includes ETag header
GET {{host}}/optional/products/{{createOptional.response.body.id}}

### 3. Conditional GET — If-None-Match → 304 Not Modified
GET {{host}}/optional/products/{{createOptional.response.body.id}}
If-None-Match: "{{createOptional.response.body.eTag}}"

### 4. Update WITH If-Match → 200 OK + new ETag
PUT {{host}}/optional/products/{{createOptional.response.body.id}}
Content-Type: application/json
If-Match: "{{createOptional.response.body.eTag}}"

{
  "price": 39.99
}

### 5. Update with STALE If-Match → 412 Precondition Failed
# @expect status: 412
PUT {{host}}/optional/products/{{createOptional.response.body.id}}
Content-Type: application/json
If-Match: "stale-etag-value"

{
  "price": 49.99
}

### 6. Update WITHOUT If-Match → 200 OK (unconditional, allowed)
PUT {{host}}/optional/products/{{createOptional.response.body.id}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "price": 59.99
}

### ══════════════════════════════════════════════
### REQUIRED If-Match (/required/products)
### Updates WITHOUT If-Match get 428
### ══════════════════════════════════════════════

### 7. Create a product
# @name createRequired
POST {{host}}/required/products
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Gadget",
  "price": 49.99
}

### 8. Get the product — response includes ETag header
GET {{host}}/required/products/{{createRequired.response.body.id}}

### 9. Update WITH If-Match → 200 OK + new ETag
PUT {{host}}/required/products/{{createRequired.response.body.id}}
Content-Type: application/json
If-Match: "{{createRequired.response.body.eTag}}"

{
  "price": 59.99
}

### 10. Update WITHOUT If-Match → 428 Precondition Required
# @expect status: 428
PUT {{host}}/required/products/{{createRequired.response.body.id}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "price": 69.99
}

### 11. Update with STALE If-Match → 412 Precondition Failed
# @expect status: 412
PUT {{host}}/required/products/{{createRequired.response.body.id}}
Content-Type: application/json
If-Match: "stale-etag-value"

{
  "price": 79.99
}

### 12. If-Match wildcard → 200 OK (matches any ETag)
PUT {{host}}/required/products/{{createRequired.response.body.id}}
Content-Type: application/json
If-Match: *

{
  "price": 89.99
}
